trans-unit.source: Generates proxy class code for Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) services
trans-unit.target: Genererer proxy-klassekode for Windows Communication Foundation (WCF)-tjenester

trans-unit.source: The WCFBuildProvider uses mapping files (.svcmap) at the root level of the Web application that contains WCF service references.
trans-unit.target: WCFBuildProvider bruker tilordningsfilene (.svcmap) på root-nivå for webprogram som inneholder referanser for WCF-tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The mapping files specify the services for which proxy class source code must be generated.
trans-unit.target: Tilordningsfilene angi tjenestene som kildekode for proxy-klassen må genereres.

trans-unit.source: The generated proxy class is then compiled with the other resources during the Web application compilation phase.
trans-unit.target: Generert proxy-klassen er deretter kompilert med de andre ressursene fasen for kompilering av nettserveren.

trans-unit.source: The inherited <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.VirtualPath%2A> property is internally defined and points to the Web application root directory where the .svcmap files reside.
trans-unit.target: Arvet <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.VirtualPath%2A>egenskapen defineres internt og peker til Web rotkatalogen der .svcmap-filene er lagret.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.VirtualPath%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.WCFBuildProvider"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.WCFBuildProvider"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Generates the service proxy class source code and adds it to the specified assembly builder.
trans-unit.target: Genererer kildekode for tjenesten proxy-klassen og legger til den angitte samlingen-verktøyet.

trans-unit.source: This method searches for .svcmap files in the Web application root directory.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden søker etter .svcmap filer i rotmappen for Web-programmet.

trans-unit.source: If files are found, the method generates the source code of a proxy class for the related services into the specified `assemblyBuilder`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis filene finnes, metoden genererer kildekode av en proxy-klasse for tjenestene som er relatert til det angitte `assemblyBuilder`.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder> object that the generated proxy code must be added to.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av den <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder>objektet generert proxy-koden må legges til.</xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder>

trans-unit.source: This instance is provided by ASP.NET at run time.
trans-unit.target: Denne forekomsten er angitt av ASP.NET ved kjøretid.
